node.text: Kristen Hanby hangs out with his niece Lexi! What would she eat if she could only eat one food for the rest of her life? Who would she freeze in a block of solid ice? Who is her best friend? Check out this adorable interview with the youngest Hanby in this week’s episode of Get To Know The Family.

node.text: Kristen Hanby sits down with his cousin Liv! Who are some of her favorite celebrities? Which super power would she pick? Will she ever answer a single question? Tune in for another interview full of laughs, slaps, and awkward silence in this week’s episode of Get To Know The Family.

node.text: Kristen Hanby sits down with his sister, Bryony! Who knows what she would do if she was an elephant, or what her on the spot jokes are in a life of death situation!? In another episode of Get To Know The Family, dive into Kristen’s relationship with Bryony and get to know her better.
